title: Me First and the Gimme Gimmes - 2008 - Have Another Ball [FLAC]
description:
Have Another Ball is a compilation album by the punk rock cover band Me First and the Gimme Gimmes. It is their seventh album overall, and was released on July 8, 2008 by Fat Wreck Chords.

The album features a-sides dating back to before their first album, Have a Ball. Many of the tracks were previously released on now out-of-print 7" vinyl singles, while others were featured on compilation albums.

Track Listing
01 - Rich Girl (Hall & Oates cover)
02 - The Boxer (Simon and Garfunkel cover)
03 - Country Roads (John Denver cover)
04 - I Write the Songs (Barry Manilow cover)
05 - Sodomy (Hair Cast cover)
06 - You've Got a Friend (James Taylor cover)
07 - Mahogany (Diana Ross cover)
08 - Mother and Child Reunion (Paul Simon cover)
09 - Only the Good Die Young (Billy Joel cover)
10 - Coming to America (Neil Diamond cover)
11 - The Harder They Come (Jimmy Cliff cover)
12 - Don't Let the Sun Go Down on Me (Elton John cover)

All tracks are DRM-free and encoded losslessly in FLAC format (16 bit, stereo, 44.1 kHz). For more information about FLAC visit http://flac.sourceforge.net/. Album summary courtesy of Wikipedia and is available under the terms of the GNU Free Documentation License.
